ck_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-5Ms","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":23479,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/07\/12\/not-one-of-us-bad-akhlaq\/","url_meta":{"origin":22224,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Character: He is not one of us who is rude, cruel","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 12, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe most complete of believers in faith are those with the best character, careful around others, friendly and befriended. He is not one of us who is neither friendly, nor befriended.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1841,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/01\/15\/allah-helps-brother\/","url_meta":{"origin":22224,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Brotherhood: Allah helps him as long as he helps his brother","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever relieves the hardship of a believer in this world, Allah will relieve his hardship on the Day of Resurrection. Whoever helps ease one in difficulty, Allah will make it easy for him in this world\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33788,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/11\/20\/tawus-on-moderation\/","url_meta":{"origin":22224,"position":2},"title":"Tawus on Moderation: Tawus steers people towards a middle way","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 20, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Layth reported: Tawus, may Allah have mercy on him, if the people became too strict in a matter, he would grant them a concessions in it. If the people became too permissive in a matter, he would make them be more strict in it. Layth said, \u201cThat is truly knowledge.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18108,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/11\/beat-people-beneficial\/","url_meta":{"origin":22224,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Friendliness: Best people are kind, benefit others","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 11, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe believer is friendly and befriended, for there is no goodness in one who is neither friendly nor befriended. The best of people are those who are most beneficial to people.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 5937 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26964,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/12\/30\/hasan-believers-continue-repent\/","url_meta":{"origin":22224,"position":4},"title":"Hasan on Repentance: Believers continue to repent again and again","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 30, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Sufyan al-Thawri reported: It was said to Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, regarding a man who sins and then repents, then sins and repents three more times. Hasan said, \"These are the manners of the believer.\" Source: al-Waji\u0304z fi\u0304 Dhikr al-Maja\u0304z 17 \u0639\u0646 \u0633\u064f\u0641\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062b\u064e\u0651\u0648\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a \u200f\u0642\u064a\u0644 \u0644\u0644\u062d\u0633\u0646\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20860,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/09\/01\/hasan-everyday-obey-eid\/","url_meta":{"origin":22224,"position":5},"title":"Hasan on Eid: Every day Muslims obey Allah a celebration","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 1, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Rajab reported: Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cEvery day in which Allah is not disobeyed is a celebration. Every day the believer spends in obedience, servitude, remembrance, and gratitude is a celebration.\u201d Source: Lat\u0323a\u0304'if al-Ma'a\u0304rif 1\/278 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0631\u062c\u0628 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0633\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0635\u0631\u064a \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u062a\u0639\u0627\u0644\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/22224","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=22224"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/22224\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=22224"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=22224"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=22224"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}